translations: 反坦克航空火箭（Antitank Aircraft Rocket）

sentences.sentence: Hundreds of fans crowded onto the airfield to wait for the famous film atar.
sentences.translation: 上百名影迷拥在停机坪上等待著名的影星。

sentences.sentence: These ICF courses are classified as category B subjects and only two units of these may be used in the calculation of the ATAR.
sentences.translation: 这些ICF 课程被归类为B 范畴学科，在这些课程中，仅有两 个被用在ATAR 的估算。
